---
import PortalLayout from '~/layouts/PortalLayout.astro';
---
<PortalLayout title="Home" active="home">
  <h1>TNMAN 2026 Field Portal</h1>
  <p class="muted">
    13–15 MAY 26 · Holston AAP, Kingsport TN · Tennessee State Guard, 3 RGT
  </p>

  <div class="card">
    <h2 style="margin-top:0">Start Here</h2>
    <p>
      This portal is the field-side companion to the planning site. Your role guide
      tells you what's expected; this app captures your activity log and AAR notes.
    </p>
    <ol>
      <li>Open <a href="/guides">Participant Guides</a> and read your role page.</li>
      <li>Review <a href="/guides/common">Common Expectations</a> — applies to everyone.</li>
      <li>Install and verify <a href="/guides/caltopo">CalTopo</a> before 12 MAY.</li>
      <li>Log your activity each day at <a href="/log">214 Log</a>.</li>
      <li>Capture observations as they happen at <a href="/aar">AAR</a>.</li>
    </ol>
  </div>

  <div class="card">
    <h2 style="margin-top:0">Quick Actions</h2>
    <div class="row">
      <a class="btn primary" href="/log">Log a 214 entry</a>
      <a class="btn teal" href="/aar">Record an AAR observation</a>
      <a class="btn" href="/injects">Active injects</a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="card">
    <h2 style="margin-top:0">Where to Get Help</h2>
    <ul class="list-tight">
      <li><strong>Role-specific clarification:</strong> your Section Chief.</li>
      <li><strong>ICS / docs / process:</strong> 1LT Overton (Planning Section Chief).</li>
      <li><strong>Personnel / orders / sign-in:</strong> 1LT Fielitz-Scarbrough (RUL).</li>
      <li><strong>Safety / hydration / MRC:</strong> SFC Sturgill (Safety Officer).</li>
      <li><strong>Medical:</strong> MAJ Gampe (Medical Unit).</li>
      <li><strong>Comms / WINLINK:</strong> CSM Rutherford (Comms Unit).</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <p class="muted small">
    Planner site (orders, graphics, full reference): <a href="https://tnman-2026.web.app">tnman-2026.web.app</a>.
  </p>
</PortalLayout>
